---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Repuso — Testimonial Widget Comparison | SocialProof" description="Repuso pulls reviews from third-party platforms. SocialProof collects your own testimonials directly from customers — free to start, $9/mo Pro. Honest comparison for small businesses." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/repuso">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0 1rem; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .bottom-cta a { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #aaa; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } }
</style>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/vs/">Compare</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs Repuso</div>
  <h1>A simpler alternative to <span>Repuso</span></h1>
  <p>Repuso aggregates reviews from Google, Facebook, and Yelp. SocialProof collects your own testimonials directly from customers — no platform dependency, yours to own forever.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch">
      <div class="price">Free</div>
      <div class="label">SocialProof starter</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item other">
      <div class="price">$9+/mo</div>
      <div class="label">Repuso starting price</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Repuso</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Free plan</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Free forever (1 widget)</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Paid only</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Free / $9/mo Pro</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">$9+/mo (no free tier)</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Collect testimonials directly</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Shareable collection link</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Pulls from 3rd-party platforms only</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Own your testimonials</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Data is yours, always</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">~ Dependent on platform APIs</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Works without Google/Facebook account</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Fully standalone</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Requires review platform connection</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embed widget</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ One script tag</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Schema markup (SEO)</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Built in</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">~ Limited</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>No-code setup</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Paste 1 script tag</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Custom branding</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Pro plan</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Moderation controls</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Approve before display</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">~ Platform-level only</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>The key difference: owned vs. borrowed</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.7;">
    Repuso is built around aggregating reviews you didn't originally collect — pulling from Google, Facebook, Yelp, and other platforms. That's useful if you already have a review presence there. But it means your testimonials live on someone else's platform, subject to their API changes, policies, and availability.
    <br /><br />
    SocialProof works differently: you send customers a direct link, they write a testimonial, you approve it, it appears on your site. The testimonials are yours — not dependent on any third-party platform staying online or keeping your access active.
  </p>

  <h2>Who wins for small businesses?</h2>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✓ SocialProof is better if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Want to collect original testimonials directly from customers</li>
        <li>Don't have an established Google/Facebook review presence yet</li>
        <li>Want full ownership and control of your testimonials</li>
        <li>Need a free starting point with no credit card</li>
        <li>Care about schema markup for Google rich snippets</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Repuso might be better if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Already have 50+ reviews on Google or Facebook</li>
        <li>Want to aggregate reviews from multiple platforms in one widget</li>
        <li>Primarily need to display existing third-party reviews</li>
        <li>Don't need a direct testimonial collection flow</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>💰 The math: free vs. $9+/mo</h3>
    <p>Repuso has no free plan — you're paying from day one. SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget, and only <strong>$9/mo</strong> when you need more. If you're just starting out, that's hundreds of dollars saved in year one.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>What users say</h2>
  <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; background: #f8f8ff; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #333;">
    "I tried Repuso but it kept breaking whenever Google changed something. With SocialProof I just send clients a link and the testimonials show up on my site. Much simpler."
    <div style="margin-top: .75rem; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem;">— Freelance designer</div>
  </blockquote>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>The bottom line</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.7;">
    If you want to display reviews you've already earned on Google or Yelp, Repuso can aggregate those. But if you want to <em>actively collect</em> fresh testimonials from your customers — and own that content outright — SocialProof is the better fit.
    <br /><br />
    Start free. No credit card. Your first widget is live in under 5 minutes.
  </p>

  <div class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
    <p>Free forever for 1 widget. Upgrade to Pro ($9/mo) when you need more.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/vs/" style="color: #aaa;">Compare all tools</a></p>
</footer>
</Base>
